What's that new branch for?

https://typescript.codeplex.com/SourceControl/list/changesets?branch=FidelityGenerics

It's been created seemingly for some temporary work or what? There's only one commit, with some generic-related changes off the main develop branch.
It's just a safe place for us to do the work to get the parser using generics internally without adding risk to the develop branch right now.
